    "description": "Relax, Chill or Strive with Lofi in the world of Miszou, a 2.5d Rollerblading Platformer. Customize and make your way through the 4 unique Turtles of Miszou in whatever clothing or skating style that suits you. Listen to LoFi whilst you perform tricks and use momentum to skate, jump and grind though various levels, on the way you will meet many eccentric characters while traversing the challenging, colourful world to become the best skater in Miszou.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143020/extras/8bf0992de502229597fdf1c04d2eda51.poster.avif?t=1700059182\" width=680 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143020/extras/8bf0992de502229597fdf1c04d2eda51.webm?t=1700059182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the 4 Worlds of Miszou</h2><br>- Fishbowl <br>- Coral<br>- Reef<br>- Synthius<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Listen to LoFi</h2>Cruise through Miszou while listening to the chill LoFi tunes. All four worlds will have unique tracks complementing your journey as you roll through each level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143020/extras/d28ff55432c03d20babd9f9950c15e76.poster.avif?t=1700059182\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143020/extras/d28ff55432c03d20babd9f9950c15e76.webm?t=1700059182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143020/extras/d28ff55432c03d20babd9f9950c15e76.mp4?t=1700059182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
